{
  "texts": [
    "It was generally found that the resulting grid topology is only slightly influenced by the hyperparameters of S 3, provided they are chosen within reasonable bounds; therefore, results of conducted hyperparameter studies are not included here.",
    "A summary of all hyperparameters and their default values can be found in table (1).Table 1: Hyperparameters and associated default values for S 3.",
    "The parameters N c,start and N c,end denote the number of cells selected for refinement at the beginning and at the end of the adaptive refinement, respectively, while M represents the number of cells of the original grid.",
    "The default stopping criterion is activated when the current approximation of the metric field || M|| relative to the original metric field ||M|| exceeds the given threshold M min.",
    "N uni N c,start N c, Airfoil tandem configurationThe first test case is a tandem airfoil configuration in high-speed stall conditions."
  ]
}